/how-to-check-your-google-index-status-in-wordpress/\" title=\"How to Check Your Google Index Status in WordPress\">see your index status</a> right from your WordPress dashboard!</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"410\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/post-index-status-2-1024x410.png\" alt=\"Checking your index status in AIOSEO\'s details section.\" class=\"wp-image-245422\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/post-index-status-2-1024x410.png 1024w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/post-index-status-2-300x120.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/post-index-status-2-768x307.png 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/post-index-status-2-1536x615.png 1536w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/post-index-status-2-2048x820.png 2048w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/post-index-status-2-600x240.png 600w\" sizes=\"100vw\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>It also gives you other vital information about your URL:</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"702\" height=\"348\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/post-index-status-extra-info.png\" alt=\"AIOSEO\'s Index Status showing other important URL data.\" class=\"wp-image-245423\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/post-index-status-extra-info.png 702w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/post-index-status-extra-info-300x149.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/post-index-status-extra-info-600x297.png 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 702px) 100vw, 702px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>All this helps ensure you know which pages are indexed so you can better troubleshoot those that havent been indexed.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"aioseo-2-optimize-your-sitemaps\">2. Optimize Your Sitemaps</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>If you want search engines and users to find your posts and pages easily, you must create an optimized XML sitemap.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"535\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/example-xml-sitemap-1024x535.png\" alt=\"Example of XML sitemap\" class=\"wp-image-185484\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/example-xml-sitemap-1024x535.png 1024w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/example-xml-sitemap-300x157.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/example-xml-sitemap-768x401.png 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/example-xml-sitemap-600x313.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/example-xml-sitemap-115x60.png 115w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/example-xml-sitemap-172x90.png 172w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/example-xml-sitemap.png 1323w\" sizes=\"100vw\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>These help search engines crawl and understand your URLs better, resulting in better indexing. Dont worry if you have lots of pages on your site. AIOSEO makes it easy to <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/how-to-add-multiple-urls-to-your-sitemap-the-easy-way/\" title=\"How to Add Multiple URLs to Your Sitemap (The Easy Way)\">add multiple URLs to your sitemap</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"345\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/add-multiple-urls-to-additional-pages-1-1024x345.png\" alt=\"AIOSEO makes it easy to add multiple URLs to your sitemap.\" class=\"wp-image-99835\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/add-multiple-urls-to-additional-pages-1-1024x345.png 1024w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/add-multiple-urls-to-additional-pages-1-300x101.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/add-multiple-urls-to-additional-pages-1-768x259.png 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/add-multiple-urls-to-additional-pages-1-600x202.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/add-multiple-urls-to-additional-pages-1.png 1038w\" sizes=\"100vw\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>When you submit your sitemap to Google Search Console (GSC), you can easily monitor your URLs for performance and identify potential issues impacting your SEO.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>For more details, weve created a handy guide to help you <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/create-a-wordpress-xml-sitemap-without-a-plugin/\" title=\"How to Create a WordPress XML Sitemap Without a Plugin\">create sitemaps in WordPress</a>.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"aioseo-3-leverage-the-indexnow-protocol\">3. Leverage the IndexNow Protocol</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>The <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/what-is-indexnow-for-seo/\" title=\"What is IndexNow for SEO (Explained in Plain English)?\">IndexNow protocol</a> makes the internet more efficient by instantly alerting participating search engines of any changes you make on your website.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"700\" height=\"270\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/indexnow-activated.png\" alt=\"The IndexNow protocol helps your content get indexed faster.\" class=\"wp-image-73093\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/indexnow-activated.png 700w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/indexnow-activated-300x116.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/indexnow-activated-600x231.png 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>For example, if you change your content or add a new post or page, the IndexNow protocol will ping search engines about those changes.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Doing so will result in the search engines crawling and indexing your changes faster.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>This means IndexNow is a powerful tool to help you get your content indexed faster, resulting in better chances of ranking.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Another significant advantage of IndexNow is that if one search engine participating in the IndexNow initiative is pinged, all other search engines will be alerted when new content is published. As a result, your content will quickly appear in search results for relevant searches.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>The best part is that <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/how-to-add-indexnow-in-wordpress/\" title=\"How to Add IndexNow in WordPress (For Faster Indexing)\">adding IndexNow to your site</a> is easy.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"aioseo-4-optimize-your-robots-txt-file\">4. Optimize Your Robots.txt File</h3>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/what-is-robots-txt-in-wordpress/\" title=\"What is Robots.txt in WordPress? [Beginners Guide]\">A robots.txt file</a> is a powerful SEO tool that guides search engine crawl bots or robots on which pages to crawl. As you may have guessed, its important that your robots.txt gives Google permission to crawl most of your site.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>On the other hand, its common to disallow wp-admin pages and other pages irrelevant to your SEO strategy. Thats because they arent useful to your search strategy. Telling Google not to crawl unnecessary pages can help boost rankings in search engines and increase page speed.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"730\" height=\"280\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/aioseo-robots-txt-file.png\" alt=\"Example of a robots.txt file\" class=\"wp-image-26295\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/aioseo-robots-txt-file.png 730w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/aioseo-robots-txt-file-300x115.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/aioseo-robots-txt-file-600x230.png 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 730px) 100vw, 730px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>But when it comes to indexing in SEO, you should ensure your important pages are crawlable. You can tell Google bots to allow crawling and even prioritize these URLs.&nbsp; This is super easy to do with <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/features/robots-editor/\" title=\"Robots.txt Editor\">AIOSEOs Robots.txt Editor</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"702\" height=\"502\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/how-to-easily-edit-a-robotstxt-file-in-wordpress-1.png\" alt=\"AIOSEO\'s robots.txt editor.\" class=\"wp-image-222049\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/how-to-easily-edit-a-robotstxt-file-in-wordpress-1.png 702w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/how-to-easily-edit-a-robotstxt-file-in-wordpress-1-300x215.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/how-to-easily-edit-a-robotstxt-file-in-wordpress-1-600x429.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/how-to-easily-edit-a-robotstxt-file-in-wordpress-1-84x60.png 84w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/how-to-easily-edit-a-robotstxt-file-in-wordpress-1-126x90.png 126w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 702px) 100vw, 702px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>This powerful tool makes optimizing your robots.txt file easy as it comes with many useful directives such as Allow, Disallow, Clean-param, and Crawl-delay.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"702\" height=\"426\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/how-to-edit-robots-txt-directives.png\" alt=\"Directives in AIOSEO\'s Robots.txt Editor.\" class=\"wp-image-220372\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/how-to-edit-robots-txt-directives.png 702w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/how-to-edit-robots-txt-directives-300x182.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/how-to-edit-robots-txt-directives-600x364.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/how-to-edit-robots-txt-directives-99x60.png 99w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/how-to-edit-robots-txt-directives-148x90.png 148w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 702px) 100vw, 702px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>You also have the option to import a robots.txt file from another site, saving you a lot of time optimizing yours.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"702\" height=\"321\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/how-to-edit-robots-txt-import.png\" alt=\"Importing a robots.txt using AIOSEO.\" class=\"wp-image-220390\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/how-to-edit-robots-txt-import.png 702w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/how-to-edit-robots-txt-import-300x137.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/how-to-edit-robots-txt-import-600x274.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/how-to-edit-robots-txt-import-131x60.png 131w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/how-to-edit-robots-txt-import-197x90.png 197w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 702px) 100vw, 702px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>For more details, please visit our post on <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/how-to-edit-a-robots-txt-file-in-wordpress/\" title=\"How to Easily Edit a Robots.txt File in WordPress (Step by Step)\">how to edit a robots.txt file in WordPress</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Enhancing your sites indexing is super important to ensuring your content ranks and driving relevant traffic to your site. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>For more tips, check out our article on <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/index-your-website-on-google/\" title=\"10 Quick &amp; Easy Ways to Index Your Website on Google\">easy ways to index your site on Google</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"aioseo-what-is-indexing-your-faqs-answered\">What is Indexing? Your FAQs Answered</h2>\n\n\n\n<div data-schema-only=\"false\" class=\"wp-block-aioseo-faq\" id=\"aioseo-what-does-indexing-mean-in-seo\"><h3 class=\"aioseo-faq-block-question\">What does &#8220;indexing&#8221; mean in SEO?</h3><div class=\"aioseo-faq-block-answer\">\n<p>In SEO, indexing refers to the process in which search engines organize and store information gathered during the crawling phase. It involves creating an efficient catalog of web pages, making it easier for search engines to retrieve relevant results when users perform a search query.</p>\n</div></div>\n\n\n\n<div data-schema-only=\"false\" class=\"wp-block-aioseo-faq\" id=\"aioseo-why-is-seo-indexing-important\"><h3 class=\"aioseo-faq-block-question\">Why is indexing in SEO important?</h3><div class=\"aioseo-faq-block-answer\">\n<p>SEO indexing is crucial for visibility in search engine results. Well-indexed content is more likely to appear in search results, improving the chances of attracting organic traffic. It enhances the user experience by delivering relevant and timely results.</p>\n</div></div>\n\n\n\n<div data-schema-only=\"false\" class=\"wp-block-aioseo-faq\" id=\"aioseo-are-there-tools-that-can-help-with-indexing\"><h3 class=\"aioseo-faq-block-question\">Are There Tools that Can Help With Indexing?</h3><div class=\"aioseo-faq-block-answer\">\n<p>Yes. Tools like All In One SEO (AIOSEO) can help ensure that your site and pages get indexed. It has features like IndexNow, an advanced robots.txt editor, and much more.</p>\n</div></div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"aioseo-improve-your-indexing-boost-your-rankings\">Improve Your Indexing, Boost Your Rankings</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Now that you know what indexing is and why its important, go ahead and optimize your site for indexing by search engines. Remember, with AIOSEO, you get a lot of features and tools to help you do that.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>We hope this post helped you understand what indexing is and why its important for your SEO. You may also want to check out other articles on our blog, like our <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/best-content-optimization-tools-for-seo/\" title=\"7 Best Content Optimization Tools for SEO\">top content optimization tools</a> or our guide on <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/docs/crawl-cleanup-best-practices/\" title=\"How to Use Crawl Cleanup to Increase Search Engine Crawl Quota\">using Crawl Cleanup to boost your SEO</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>If you found this article helpful, then please subscribe to our <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/c/AIOSEO\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">YouTube Channel</a>. Youll find many more helpful tutorials there. You can also follow us on <a href=\"https://twitter.com/aioseopack\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">X (Twitter)</a>, <a href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/company/aioseo/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">LinkedIn</a>, or <a href=\"https://facebook.com/aioseopack/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">Facebook</a> to stay in the loop.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>The post <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/indexing-in-seo/\">What Is Indexing in SEO? A Beginners Guide [Plus Tips]</a> first appeared on <a href=\"https://aioseo.com\">AIOSEO</a>.\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:40:\"https://aioseo.com/indexing-in-seo/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:1;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:85:\"\n		\n		\n					\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n\n					\n										\n					\n					\n			\n		\n		\n			\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:43:\"SEO for Beginners: a Simple WordPress Guide\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:130:\"https://aioseo.com/seo-for-beginners-wordpress-guide/?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=seo-for-beginners-wordpress-guide\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:61:\"https://aioseo.com/seo-for-beginners-wordpress-guide/#respond\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Mon, 20 Nov 2023 14:00:00 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:5:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:4:\"Blog\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:1;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:8:\"SEO Tips\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:2;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:12:\"Beginner SEO\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:3;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:16:\"How to learn SEO\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:4;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:17:\"SEO for beginners\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:28:\"https://aioseo.com/?p=248333\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:435:\"<p>When you start on your digital journey, it&#8217;s essential to understand SEO for beginners. Learning SEO may seem daunting, but with the right resources, its easier than you think. Our guide is aimed at those using WordPress, one of the&#8230;</p>\nThe post <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/seo-for-beginners-wordpress-guide/\">SEO for Beginners: a Simple WordPress Guide</a> first appeared on <a href=\"https://aioseo.com\">AIOSEO</a>.\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:15:\"Sherrie Gossett\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:40604:\"<p>When you start on your digital journey, it&#8217;s essential to understand SEO for beginners.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Learning SEO may seem daunting, but with the right resources, its easier than you think.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Our guide is aimed at those using WordPress, one of the world&#8217;s most popular website platforms.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>With the help of a dedicated WordPress SEO plugin, we&#8217;ll show you how to make your site stand out, even if you&#8217;re entirely new to this field.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Welcome to your introductory guide to SEO for beginners.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Lets start by defining SEO.</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group aioseo-table-of-contents has-theme-info-background-color has-background is-layout-flow wp-block-group-is-layout-flow\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<p>In This Article</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-aioseo-table-of-contents\"><ul><li><a href=\"#aioseo-what-is-seo\">What is SEO?</a><ul></ul></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-can-i-teach-myself-seo\">Can I Teach Myself SEO?</a></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-introducing-the-focus-keyphrase\">Introducing the Focus Keyphrase</a></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-how-to-get-started-with-seo\">SEO for Beginners: How to Get Started</a><ul><li><a href=\"#aioseo-step-1-download-all-in-one-seo-aioseo\">Step 1: Download All in One SEO (AIOSEO)</a></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-step-2-optimize-your-search-snippet\">Step 2: Optimize Your Search Snippet</a><ul></ul></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-step-3-check-focus-keyphrase-use\">Step 3: Check Focus Keyphrase Use</a></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-step-4-add-links\">Step 4: Add Links</a></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-step-5-improve-readability\">Step 5: Improve Readability</a><ul></ul></li></ul></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-seo-for-beginners-achievment-unlocked\">Congratulations!</a><ul></ul></li></ul></div>\n</div></div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"aioseo-what-is-seo\">What is SEO?</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>SEO, or search engine optimization, is the art and science of creating high-quality content that attracts and satisfies users and achieves website goals.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Because all online content is indexed and ranked by search engines, learning the basics of SEO is vital to online success.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"aioseo-can-i-teach-myself-seo\">Can I Teach Myself SEO?</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Thanks to online tutorials and software, it&#8217;s never been easier to teach yourself SEO.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>You can learn SEO fundamentals quickly by using a WordPress plugin. The plugin will automate many tasks and simplify your SEO.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"aioseo-introducing-the-focus-keyphrase\">Introducing the Focus Keyphrase</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Before we start, you&#8217;ll need to know what a focus keyphrase is.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>A focus keyphrase is the <em>main topic</em> of your page. SEO will be easier if you <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/docs/using-the-focus-keyphrase-to-analyze-your-content/\">choose your focus keyphrase</a> <em>before</em> creating the related page content.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Your focus keyphrase can be one word (like &#8220;keto&#8221;). But its more effective to use a specific phrase, like &#8220;keto recipes&#8221; or &#8220;keto meal prepping.&#8221;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>After you work through this tutorial, we recommend learning the <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/seo-secrets-to-grow-revenue/\">basics of keyword research</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Learning to do this type of research will help you choose a keyword that&#8217;s <em>easy to rank for</em>. And this tactic can help you rank higher in search results.</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-aioseo-theme-notice-box\" role=\"alert\">\n<p>Other terms for focus keyphrase include focus keyword or target keyword.</p>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<p>Now, let&#8217;s get started with SEO for beginners.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"aioseo-how-to-get-started-with-seo\">SEO for Beginners: How to Get Started </h2>\n\n\n\n<p>To learn quickly and get results, we recommend using an SEO plugin.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>This is where <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/\" title=\"\">All on One SEO (AIOSEO)</a> comes in. It&#8217;s designed for beginners and makes optimizing pages simple.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>AIOSEO will analyze your pages and provide a checklist of actions.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>For each item that needs improvement, youll receive clear steps So, theres no need for guesswork.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Don&#8217;t worry: you don&#8217;t need to know code or anything technical. If you can click buttons and fill out form fields, you can use this plugin.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"485\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/aioseo-homepage-1024x485.png\" alt=\"aioseo homepage\" class=\"wp-image-140989\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/aioseo-homepage-1024x485.png 1024w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/aioseo-homepage-300x142.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/aioseo-homepage-768x364.png 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/aioseo-homepage-600x284.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/aioseo-homepage-127x60.png 127w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/aioseo-homepage-190x90.png 190w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/aioseo-homepage.png 1260w\" sizes=\"100vw\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>All in One SEO is an established plugin with thousands of 5-star reviews on WordPress.org. Currently, it&#8217;s used by over 3 million site owners.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"aioseo-step-1-download-all-in-one-seo-aioseo\">Step 1: Download All in One SEO (AIOSEO)</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>After downloading and installing All in One SEO (AIOSEO), a setup wizard will walk you through a few steps.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Now, you&#8217;re ready to take action. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>Let&#8217;s find the <strong>AIOSEO sidebar</strong>.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>In the WordPress editor, navigate to a page you want to optimize.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Then click on the <em>AIOSEO button</em> at the upper right.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full is-resized\"><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/aioseo-button.png\" alt=\"aioseo button in wordpress editor\" class=\"wp-image-248374\" style=\"width:340px;height:375px\" width=\"340\" height=\"375\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/aioseo-button.png 810w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/aioseo-button-272x300.png 272w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/aioseo-button-768x847.png 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/aioseo-button-600x661.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/aioseo-button-54x60.png 54w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/aioseo-button-82x90.png 82w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 340px) 100vw, 340px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>That will open the AIOSEO sidebar.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Next, click on <strong>General</strong>.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large is-resized\"><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/aioseo-sidebar-general-735x1024.png\" alt=\"aioseo sidebar general tab\" class=\"wp-image-248375\" style=\"width:322px;height:449px\" width=\"322\" height=\"449\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/aioseo-sidebar-general-735x1024.png 735w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/aioseo-sidebar-general-215x300.png 215w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/aioseo-sidebar-general-768x1070.png 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/aioseo-sidebar-general-600x836.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/aioseo-sidebar-general-43x60.png 43w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/aioseo-sidebar-general-65x90.png 65w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/aioseo-sidebar-general.png 798w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 322px) 100vw, 322px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Here, we&#8217;ll find AIOSEO&#8217;s action steps to improve our page&#8217;s SEO.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>We&#8217;ll start by optimizing a search snippet.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"aioseo-step-2-optimize-your-search-snippet\">Step 2: Optimize Your Search Snippet</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>First, click on the <strong>Edit Snippet</strong> button.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large is-resized\"><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/aioseo-edit-snippet-button-787x1024.png\" alt=\"aioseo edit snippet button\" class=\"wp-image-248377\" style=\"width:362px;height:471px\" width=\"362\" height=\"471\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/aioseo-edit-snippet-button-787x1024.png 787w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/aioseo-edit-snippet-button-231x300.png 231w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/aioseo-edit-snippet-button-768x999.png 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/aioseo-edit-snippet-button-600x780.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/aioseo-edit-snippet-button-46x60.png 46w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/aioseo-edit-snippet-button-69x90.png 69w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/aioseo-edit-snippet-button.png 798w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 362px) 100vw, 362px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>That will open a small popup window that shows what your page, once published, may look like in Google search results. This is called the <strong>Snippet Preview</strong>.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"258\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/aioseo-snippet-preview-example-1024x258.jpg\" alt=\"aioseo snippet preview\" class=\"wp-image-248381\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/aioseo-snippet-preview-example-1024x258.jpg 1024w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/aioseo-snippet-preview-example-300x75.jpg 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/aioseo-snippet-preview-example-768x193.jpg 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/aioseo-snippet-preview-example-1536x386.jpg 1536w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/aioseo-snippet-preview-example-2048x515.jpg 2048w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/aioseo-snippet-preview-example-600x151.jpg 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/aioseo-snippet-preview-example-190x48.jpg 190w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/aioseo-snippet-preview-example-358x90.jpg 358w\" sizes=\"100vw\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>So, what&#8217;s a search snippet? When a published web page appears in Google search results, the display is called a search snippet. A search snippet includes a title, description, and link.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Now, back in your WordPress editor, look <em>below</em> AIOSEO&#8217;s search snippet preview.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Youll see a field where you can enter a title.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Below that, theres a field to enter a description. (<em>In SEO, your page description is called a &#8220;meta description.&#8221;</em>)</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"555\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/aioseo-title-description-fields-1024x555.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-249553\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/aioseo-title-description-fields-1024x555.png 1024w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/aioseo-title-description-fields-300x163.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/aioseo-title-description-fields-768x416.png 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/aioseo-title-description-fields-1536x832.png 1536w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/aioseo-title-description-fields-2048x1110.png 2048w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/aioseo-title-description-fields-600x325.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/aioseo-title-description-fields-111x60.png 111w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/aioseo-title-description-fields-166x90.png 166w\" sizes=\"100vw\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Below each field, youll see a number. This number is the approximate character limit, after which Google <em>cuts off</em> your title or description due to space constraints.</p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li>Titles are cut off after approximately 60-65 characters.</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Meta descriptions are cut off after around 160 characters.</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<h4 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"aioseo-best-practices-for-seo-titles-and-meta-descriptions\">Best Practices for SEO Titles and Meta Descriptions</h4>\n\n\n\n<p>Because your title and description appear in search results, they&#8217;re your best opportunity to attract users to click on your page link.</p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li>Make your title and description <em>precise</em>.</li>\n\n\n\n<li>State what&#8217;s <em>unique</em> about your page.</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Include your <em>focus keyphrase</em> in both.</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Pro tip</strong>: Marketers often exceed the 60-character limit to include an extra keyword. You can choose to do the same, but remember that last keyword may wind up truncated.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Learn more about how to <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/how-to-use-a-serp-snippet-tool/#aioseo-step-3-set-your-post-title-title-tag\">set your title</a> and <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/how-to-use-a-serp-snippet-tool/#aioseo-step-4-optimize-your-meta-description\">optimize your meta description</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<h4 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"aioseo-optimize-your-url\">Optimize Your URL</h4>\n\n\n\n<p>To optimize your URL, make sure it includes your focus keyphrase.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>If your page title includes your focus keyphrase, itll <em>automatically</em> be added to your URL.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Remember: Your title, meta description, and URL should all include your focus keyphrase.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>And that brings us to our next check. All in One SEO analyzes your page for the presence of your focus keyphrase.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Let&#8217;s learn more.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"aioseo-step-3-check-focus-keyphrase-use\">Step 3: Check Focus Keyphrase Use</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Going back to the AIOSEO sidebar, click on <strong>Focus Keyphrase</strong>.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full is-resized\"><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/aioseo-focus-keyphrase.png\" alt=\"aioseo focus keyphrase\" class=\"wp-image-248384\" style=\"width:364px;height:279px\" width=\"364\" height=\"279\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/aioseo-focus-keyphrase.png 698w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/aioseo-focus-keyphrase-300x230.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/aioseo-focus-keyphrase-600x461.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/aioseo-focus-keyphrase-78x60.png 78w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/aioseo-focus-keyphrase-117x90.png 117w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 364px) 100vw, 364px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>In the blank field, enter your focus keyphrase and click the <strong>Add Focus Keyphrase</strong> button to save.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full is-resized\"><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/aioseo-focus-keyphrase-field-1.png\" alt=\"aioseo add focus keyphrase button\" class=\"wp-image-248388\" style=\"width:353px;height:160px\" width=\"353\" height=\"160\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/aioseo-focus-keyphrase-field-1.png 941w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/aioseo-focus-keyphrase-field-1-300x136.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/aioseo-focus-keyphrase-field-1-768x349.png 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/aioseo-focus-keyphrase-field-1-600x273.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/aioseo-focus-keyphrase-field-1-132x60.png 132w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/aioseo-focus-keyphrase-field-1-198x90.png 198w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 353px) 100vw, 353px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Now, AIOSEO will check to see if your focus keyphrase is included in the following areas.</p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li>Title, meta description, URL</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Some subheadings</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Some image alt attributes. (More on this later.)</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<p>If your focus keyphrase is missing from these areas, you&#8217;ll be prompted to add it.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large is-resized\"><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/aioseo-focus-keyphrase-not-in-title-1024x237.png\" alt=\"aioseo focus keyphrase analysis\" class=\"wp-image-244563\" style=\"width:418px;height:96px\" width=\"418\" height=\"96\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/aioseo-focus-keyphrase-not-in-title-1024x237.png 1024w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/aioseo-focus-keyphrase-not-in-title-300x70.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/aioseo-focus-keyphrase-not-in-title-768x178.png 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/aioseo-focus-keyphrase-not-in-title-600x139.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/aioseo-focus-keyphrase-not-in-title-190x44.png 190w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/aioseo-focus-keyphrase-not-in-title-388x90.png 388w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/aioseo-focus-keyphrase-not-in-title.png 1105w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 418px) 100vw, 418px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"aioseo-step-4-add-links\">Step 4: Add Links</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Returning to the AIOSEO sidebar, let&#8217;s click on <strong>Basic SEO</strong>.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Here, you&#8217;ll see a recap of the previously discussed items. And 2 link items.</p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li>Internal links</li>\n\n\n\n<li>External links</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<p>Adding relevant internal links to your page can help visitors find what they want.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>In addition, internal links can help pages <em>rank higher</em>.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>If your page has no internal links, AIOSEO will prompt you to add at least 1.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full is-resized\"><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/aioseo-internal-links-check.png\" alt=\"aioseo internal links analysis\" class=\"wp-image-248390\" style=\"width:448px;height:129px\" width=\"448\" height=\"129\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/aioseo-internal-links-check.png 951w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/aioseo-internal-links-check-300x86.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/aioseo-internal-links-check-768x220.png 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/aioseo-internal-links-check-600x172.png 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 448px) 100vw, 448px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>What about external links? External links (links to other websites) are not ranking factors. But, if you&#8217;re sharing statistics, claims, or quotations, citing your sources via a link can help generate trust in your content &#8212; <em>if the link is to a trustworthy site</em>.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>While AIOSEO will check your page for the presence of external links, it&#8217;s not mandatory to add them. Use your judgment. Consider whats helpful to the reader.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Okay, now that you&#8217;ve optimized your search snippet, checked focus keyphrase use, and added an internal link or 2, what&#8217;s next?</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Lets do a readability check.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"aioseo-step-5-improve-readability\">Step 5: Improve Readability</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>All in One SEO&#8217;s readability checks will ensure your content&#8217;s easy to read online and<a href=\"https://aioseo.com/how-to-create-scannable-content/\"> formatted for scanning</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>This means using <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/george-orwells-6-rules-for-writing/\" title=\"\">plain language</a> and breaking up long text passages with subheadings, images, or other items that make reading on digital screens more pleasant.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>In the AIOSEO sidebar, click on <strong>Readability.</strong></p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full is-resized\"><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/aioseo-readability.png\" alt=\"aioseo sidebar readability tab seo for beginners\" class=\"wp-image-248393\" style=\"width:376px;height:277px\" width=\"376\" height=\"277\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/aioseo-readability.png 698w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/aioseo-readability-300x222.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/aioseo-readability-600x444.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/aioseo-readability-81x60.png 81w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/aioseo-readability-122x90.png 122w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 376px) 100vw, 376px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Here, you&#8217;ll see what you&#8217;re doing well.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full is-resized\"><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/aioseo-readability-correct-items.png\" alt=\"aioseo readability checked items\" class=\"wp-image-248397\" style=\"width:377px;height:267px\" width=\"377\" height=\"267\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/aioseo-readability-correct-items.png 659w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/aioseo-readability-correct-items-300x213.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/aioseo-readability-correct-items-600x425.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/aioseo-readability-correct-items-85x60.png 85w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/aioseo-readability-correct-items-127x90.png 127w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 377px) 100vw, 377px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>And what could use improvement.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Below, AIOSEO tells us we have a long text passage that needs another subheading.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full is-resized\"><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/subheading-distribution.png\" alt=\"aioseo subheading distribution\" class=\"wp-image-226707\" style=\"width:416px;height:169px\" width=\"416\" height=\"169\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/subheading-distribution.png 963w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/subheading-distribution-300x121.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/subheading-distribution-768x311.png 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/subheading-distribution-600x243.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/subheading-distribution-148x60.png 148w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/subheading-distribution-222x90.png 222w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 416px) 100vw, 416px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Click the eye icon, and the portion of text that needs a new subheading will be highlighted in blue.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large is-resized\"><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/truseo-highlighter-subheadings-example-1024x386.png\" alt=\"aioseo subheading distribution floating toolbar\" class=\"wp-image-248408\" style=\"width:623px;height:235px\" width=\"623\" height=\"235\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/truseo-highlighter-subheadings-example-1024x386.png 1024w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/truseo-highlighter-subheadings-example-300x113.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/truseo-highlighter-subheadings-example-768x290.png 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/truseo-highlighter-subheadings-example-1536x580.png 1536w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/truseo-highlighter-subheadings-example-600x226.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/truseo-highlighter-subheadings-example-159x60.png 159w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/truseo-highlighter-subheadings-example-239x90.png 239w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/truseo-highlighter-subheadings-example.png 1903w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 623px) 100vw, 623px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>You can immediately locate the passage that needs another subheading.</p>\n\n\n\n<h4 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"aioseo-whats-included-in-the-readability-checks\">What&#8217;s Included in the Readability Checks?</h4>\n\n\n\n<p>Curious what&#8217;s included in the readability checks? All in One SEO will analyze these  items:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Images/videos</strong> in content: Relevant media can add value and break up long text passages.</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Length of paragraphs and sentences</strong>: Short paragraphs and sentences are easier to read.</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Passive voice</strong>: You&#8217;ll be prompted to change instances of the passive voice to the active voice.</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Transition words</strong>: If these are absent, you&#8217;ll be encouraged to add some.</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Consecutive sentences</strong> that begin with the same word: This can make a page awkward or boring to read.</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Subheading distribution</strong>: You&#8217;ll be prompted to add subheadings to long text passages. This makes reading on digital screens easier.</li>\n\n\n\n<li><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/how-to-use-the-flesch-reading-ease-score-to-grow-traffic/\"><strong>Flesch Reading Ease Score</strong></a>: The higher the score, the better.</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full is-resized\"><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/flesch-reading-ease-score.png\" alt=\"aioseo flesch reading ease score\" class=\"wp-image-248399\" style=\"width:419px;height:171px\" width=\"419\" height=\"171\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/flesch-reading-ease-score.png 765w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/flesch-reading-ease-score-300x123.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/flesch-reading-ease-score-600x245.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/flesch-reading-ease-score-147x60.png 147w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/flesch-reading-ease-score-220x90.png 220w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 419px) 100vw, 419px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"aioseo-seo-for-beginners-achievment-unlocked\">Congratulations!</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Congratulations! You&#8217;ve completed this SEO for beginners tutorial.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Remember: simply check the AIOSEO sidebar and follow the instructions. As you act on the plugin&#8217;s recommendations, you&#8217;ll see your SEO score go up. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>This reinforces good SEO habits. At the same time you&#8217;ll be learning SEO by doing it.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Before we move on to Q&amp;A, let&#8217;s look at how you can ensure your pages look great on social media.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"aioseo-optimize-your-page-for-social-media\">Optimize Your Page for Social Media</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Have you ever shared a page on social media only to be disappointed because something was missing? Maybe no image displayed. Or the description was missing.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>With All in One SEO, you can control how your pages appear on social media.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>It&#8217;s easy. Follow these instructions to <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/facebook-og-debugger-guide-for-wordpress-users/\" title=\"optimize your page for Facebook and Twitter\">optimize your page for Facebook and Twitter</a>. </p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"aioseo-qa-on-seo-for-beginners\">Q&amp;A on SEO for Beginners</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>You probably have lots of questions about SEO. Weve answered some of the most common questions we receive from beginners.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>If you have another question, please share it in the comments below. Our team of SEO professionals will be delighted to be of assistance.</p>\n\n\n\n<div data-schema-only=\"false\" class=\"wp-block-aioseo-faq\" id=\"aioseo-do-i-need-a-sitemap\"><h3 class=\"aioseo-faq-block-question\">Do I need a sitemap?</h3><div class=\"aioseo-faq-block-answer\">\n<p>Adding a sitemap to your website is a best practice. Creating and regularly updating a sitemap can help Google discover and index your site content.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Google <a href=\"https://developers.google.com/search/docs/crawling-indexing/sitemaps/build-sitemap\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">recommends</a> using 2 sitemaps: an XML sitemap and an RSS sitemap. An XML sitemap is a complete listing, in XML code, of all your site content. An RSS sitemap is smaller and lists only recently modified or newly published content. Google will crawl your RSS sitemap quickly and more frequently than your XML sitemap.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>All in One SEO (AIOSEO) automatically generates (and updates) XML and RSS sitemaps for you. No further action is needed on your part, but we do recommend <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/how-to-submit-a-sitemap-to-google-wordpress-tutorial/\">submitting your sitemap to Google</a>.</p>\n</div></div>\n\n\n\n<div data-schema-only=\"false\" class=\"wp-block-aioseo-faq\" id=\"aioseo-can-i-learn-seo-in-a-week\"><h3 class=\"aioseo-faq-block-question\">Can I learn SEO in a week?</h3><div class=\"aioseo-faq-block-answer\">\n<p>You can learn basic SEO in a week using an SEO plugin like All in One SEO (AIOSEO). The plugin will guide you and handle technical tasks for you.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Keep in mind that SEO has a range of practices, from basic to advanced. For instance, some SEO professionals specialize in creating content that generates revenue. Other SEO professionals are software engineers who solve complex code issues. Naturally, advanced skills cant be learned in a week.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>That said, if you commit to using an SEO plugin like All in One SEO, following the basics will yield surprising results.</p>\n</div></div>\n\n\n\n<div data-schema-only=\"false\" class=\"wp-block-aioseo-faq\" id=\"aioseo-can-i-learn-seo-without-coding\"><h3 class=\"aioseo-faq-block-question\">Can I learn SEO without coding?</h3><div class=\"aioseo-faq-block-answer\">\n<p>Yes, you can learn SEO without coding. Software plugins, such as All on One SEO (AIOSEO), execute SEO-related code for you while you simply click buttons and fill out form fields.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>It&#8217;s unnecessary to know code or have any technical knowledge to optimize pages for SEO.</p>\n</div></div>\n\n\n\n<div data-schema-only=\"false\" class=\"wp-block-aioseo-faq\" id=\"aioseo-what-are-rich-snippets\"><h3 class=\"aioseo-faq-block-question\">What are rich snippets?</h3><div class=\"aioseo-faq-block-answer\">\n<p><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/how-to-add-rich-snippets-to-wordpress/\" title=\"\">Rich snippets</a> are web pages that have schema markup code added to them. This code adds invisible tags to your content to help Google understand it better. As a result, your page becomes eligible to be displayed as a rich snippet in Google search engine results pages (SERPs.) Additionally, it may rank for more keywords.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Many (but not all) rich snippets appear as large search engine displays. For example, here&#8217;s a standard search snippet.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"196\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/leather-jacket-standard-search-snippet-1024x196.png\" alt=\"standard search snippet example\" class=\"wp-image-237132\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/leather-jacket-standard-search-snippet-1024x196.png 1024w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/leather-jacket-standard-search-snippet-300x58.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/leather-jacket-standard-search-snippet-768x147.png 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/leather-jacket-standard-search-snippet-600x115.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/leather-jacket-standard-search-snippet-190x36.png 190w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/leather-jacket-standard-search-snippet-469x90.png 469w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/leather-jacket-standard-search-snippet.png 1163w\" sizes=\"100vw\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>And here&#8217;s a rich snippet.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"446\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/overland-rich-snippets-leather-1024x446.jpg\" alt=\"rich snippet example overland sheepskin coats\" class=\"wp-image-212247\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/overland-rich-snippets-leather-1024x446.jpg 1024w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/overland-rich-snippets-leather-300x131.jpg 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/overland-rich-snippets-leather-768x334.jpg 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/overland-rich-snippets-leather-600x261.jpg 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/overland-rich-snippets-leather-138x60.jpg 138w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/overland-rich-snippets-leather-207x90.jpg 207w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/overland-rich-snippets-leather.jpg 1367w\" sizes=\"100vw\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>There are many styles of rich snippets for products like these, which look similar to ads. </p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"564\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/leather-jacket-rich-snippet-1024x564.jpg\" alt=\"rich snippet ecommerce example\" class=\"wp-image-183115\" title=\"example of rich snippet in google search\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/leather-jacket-rich-snippet-1024x564.jpg 1024w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/leather-jacket-rich-snippet-300x165.jpg 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/leather-jacket-rich-snippet-768x423.jpg 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/leather-jacket-rich-snippet-1536x846.jpg 1536w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/leather-jacket-rich-snippet-2048x1127.jpg 2048w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/leather-jacket-rich-snippet-600x330.jpg 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/leather-jacket-rich-snippet-109x60.jpg 109w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/leather-jacket-rich-snippet-163x90.jpg 163w\" sizes=\"100vw\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Some rich snippets will add only a small amount of extra information to search results. But it&#8217;s still worth using rich snippets because they help your page rank for relevant queries and <a href=\"https://blog.milestoneinternet.com/seo/seo-click-curves-get-58-clicks-per-100/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">attract more click-throughs</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"aioseo-how-can-i-get-rich-snippets\">How can I get rich snippets?</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>The easiest way to turn your web page into a rich snippet is to use an SEO plugin like All in One SEO (AIOSEO).</p>\n\n\n\n<p>You&#8217;ll click a few buttons and fill out some form fields. The plugin gives you a choice of different schema types to add, like book, event, courses, datasets, and more. Learn <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/how-to-add-rich-snippets-to-wordpress/\">how to use AIOSEO to add rich snippets</a>.</p>\n</div></div>\n\n\n\n<div data-schema-only=\"false\" class=\"wp-block-aioseo-faq\" id=\"aioseo-what-is-on-page-seo\"><h3 class=\"aioseo-faq-block-question\">What is on-page SEO?</h3><div class=\"aioseo-faq-block-answer\">\n<p>On-page SEO is a term marketers use to describe optimizing a single page to perform better in search engine results. It entails best practices for titles, meta descriptions, links, and keyword use.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>SEO plugins like All in One SEO (AIOSEO) include readability checks. These checks guide users to create content that&#8217;s easy and enjoyable to read online. While content quality is the #1 ranking factor, readability may not directly impact SEO. However, <a href=\"https://www.nngroup.com/articles/measuring-the-usability-of-reading-on-the-web/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">research has shown</a> it significantly impacts engagement and reader satisfaction.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>On-page SEO is the opposite of <em>off-page</em> SEO. The latter describes digital PR tactics that may help pages rank and drive traffic. These tactics include acquiring customer reviews, backlinks, and mentions in major media.</p>\n</div></div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"aioseo-what-is-on-page-seo\">Resources on SEO for Beginners</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>We&#8217;re confident you&#8217;ll catch on fast as you use the All in One SEO plugin. Once you have these basics down, you may be wondering what to work on next. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>Here are some articles and videos that provide SEO for beginners tutorials.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>SEO for Beginners Articles</strong>:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/diy-seo-projects-for-beginners/\">DIY SEO: 4 Easy Projects to Get Started</a></li>\n\n\n\n<li><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/seo-tutorial/\">A Simple SEO Tutorial for Beginners</a></li>\n\n\n\n<li><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/how-to-use-the-flesch-reading-ease-score-to-grow-traffic/\">How to Use the Flesch Reading Score to Grow Traffic</a></li>\n\n\n\n<li><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/george-orwells-6-rules-for-writing/\">George Orwell&#8217;s 6 Rules for Writing</a></li>\n\n\n\n<li><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/how-to-create-scannable-content/\">How to Create Scannable Content (an SEO Action Guide)</a></li>\n\n\n\n<li><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/seo-vs-social-media/\">SEO vs. Social Media: How Do Their Roles Differ in Digital Marketing?</a></li>\n\n\n\n<li><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/facebook-vs-website-which-is-best-for-small-business/\">Facebook vs. Website: Which is Best for Small Business?</a></li>\n\n\n\n<li><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/seo-secrets-to-grow-revenue/\">7 Secrets Used by the Pros to Grow Revenue</a></li>\n\n\n\n<li><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/small-business-seo-scams-how-to-detect-and-avoid-them/\">SEO Scams: How to Detect and Avoid Them</a></li>\n\n\n\n<li><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/referring-domains-vs-backlinks-seo/\">Referring Domains vs Backlinks: Whats the Difference?</a></li>\n\n\n\n<li><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/what-is-anchor-text-and-how-does-it-impact-seo/\">What is Anchor Text and How Does it Impact SEO?</a></li>\n\n\n\n<li><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/keyword-difficulty-in-seo-what-is-it-and-how-to-use-it/\">Keyword Difficulty in SEO: What is it and How to Use it</a></li>\n\n\n\n<li><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/how-to-create-seo-sops/\">How to Create SEO SOPs to Boost Your Organic Traffic</a></li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>SEO for Beginners</strong> <strong>Videos</strong>:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=dO5jK_Jh2uo\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">3 Ways to Get More Traffic to Your Website</a></li>\n\n\n\n<li><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3lIGi06dnzQ&amp;t=2s\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">3 Social Media Hacks to Bring You More Traffic</a></li>\n\n\n\n<li><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=mtTD3uJ5e7k\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">How to Improve the Readability of Your Site</a></li>\n\n\n\n<li><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=2wVLblO7smk\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">Take Control of How Your Website Appears on Facebook</a></li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"aioseo-what-comes-after-seo-for-beginners\">What Comes After SEO for Beginners?</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Once you&#8217;re ready to move on from SEO for beginners to intermediate-level tactics, here are some areas to consider exploring.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Link Building</strong>: When trusted sites link to yours, those <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/referring-domains-vs-backlinks-seo/\">backlinks</a> may boost your rankings, traffic, and revenue. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>Read our <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/link-building-guide/\">Ultimate Guide to Link Building</a> for ideas on getting backlinks.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Keyword Research</strong>: We mentioned that doing keyword research can help your pages rank higher. This is particularly true if you choose keywords that are easy to rank for.</p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li>Learn how to <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/keyword-difficulty-in-seo-what-is-it-and-how-to-use-it/\">check keyword difficulty scores</a>.</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Explore this <a href=\"https://www.blogtyrant.com/how-to-easily-find-the-best-keywords/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">beginners guide to keyword research</a>.</li>\n\n\n\n<li>And get a simple introduction to <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/seo-secrets-to-grow-revenue/\">search intent</a>.</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Tutorials</strong>: Subsrcibe to our <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/c/AIOSEO\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">YouTube Channel</a> for new tutorials each week. These are short and easy-to-understand. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>Also follow us on <a href=\"https://twitter.com/aioseopack\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">X (Twitter)</a>, <a href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/company/aioseo/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">LinkedIn</a>, or <a href=\"https://facebook.com/aioseopack/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">Facebook</a> to stay in the loop.</p>The post <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/seo-for-beginners-wordpress-guide/\">SEO for Beginners: a Simple WordPress Guide</a> first appeared on <a href=\"https://aioseo.com\">AIOSEO</a>.\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:58:\"https://aioseo.com/seo-for-beginners-wordpress-guide/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:2;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:82:\"\n		\n		\n					\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n		\n		\n\n					\n										\n					\n					\n			\n		\n		\n			\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:50:\"How to Check Your Google Index Status in WordPress\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:164:\"https://aioseo.com/how-to-check-your-google-index-status-in-wordpress/?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=how-to-check-your-google-index-status-in-wordpress\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17: